summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 64E & 71E, page 156 & 170, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Blocks 1 and 2, Boitano's Addition; Lots 2, 4 and 5, and portion of Lots 3, 6 and 7 westerly from Albro Place, Horton's 1st Addition, located in area bounded by Ellis Ave., Albro Place, alley west 13th Ave. South, and alley between Angelo St. and Bailey St., as Community Business (BC) Zone.
